name: "Portrait" of Lady Corvina, Countess of Cawe
description:
A portrait of a noblewoman who may have existed in a far-off fantasy land. This is the first of a series of pieces exploring anthropomorphic subjects in well-known art motifs. All sources licensed through Unsplash, Pexels, or Public Domain.
